dismissalText.commentary: Mark Boucher c Ambrose b McGarrell 10 (6b 1x4 0x6 20m) SR: 166.66

notes: Game re-scheduled for 46 overs/side after 92 minutes lost through rain
Rain fell again with West Indies 3/0 after 3 overs, and on restart overs were reduced to 28 overs/side (225 minutes lost)
South Africa were fined 1 over for a slow over rate
South Africa target revised to 160 off 27 overs (Duckworth-Lewis method)

milestones.description: Ambrose has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 205 wickets, going past Walsh's 204
